Dialogue: 30,0:00:05.54,0:00:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari-chan?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:08.50,0:00:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari-chan?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari-chan!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:18.60,0:00:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:19.85,0:00:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:24.39,0:00:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is my treatment for today all done?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:27.27,0:00:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! You did great today!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a good girl!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:32.74,0:00:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for the good girl Kagari-chan,\NI have some special news!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:37.74,0:00:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,News?
Dialogue: 30,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:40.29,0:00:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the paperwork is finally out of the way.
Dialogue: 30,0:00:43.41,0:00:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that it took so long,\Nbut starting today...
Dialogue: 30,0:00:47.46,0:00:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I get to be your real mommy!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:50.71,0:00:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can live together now!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:57.01,0:00:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 30,0:00:59.10,0:01:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! You're such a spoiled one, Kagari-chan!
Dialogue: 30,0:01:05.73,0:01:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ There's just one thing I'm searching for... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:01:11.65,0:01:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The laughter of the stars. ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:01:16.10,0:01:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What song is that?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:17.99,0:01:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:19.53,0:01:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you asked.\NIt's a very precious song to me.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:23.12,0:01:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:24.54,0:01:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 30,0:01:26.00,0:01:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to this song that Mommy\Nand Kagari-chan were able to meet.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:30.54,0:01:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:31.59,0:01:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! That's why you should give it\Nyour best and try to memorize it too!
Dialogue: 30,0:01:36.72,0:01:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because someday, you'll meet\Nsomebody precious to you too.
Dialogue: 30,0:01:41.26,0:01:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn that song too!\NTeach me Mommy's precious song!
Dialogue: 30,0:01:46.85,0:01:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Should we sing it together?
Dialogue: 30,0:01:48.94,0:01:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 30,0:01:53.28,0:01:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ There's just one thing I'm searching for... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:01:59.36,0:02:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ There's just one thing I'm searching for... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:02:03.29,0:02:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! Good, good!
Dialogue: 30,0:02:05.20,0:02:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The laughter of the stars... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:02:10.96,0:02:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The laughter of the stars... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:02:16.97,0:02:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Twinkling in the wind... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:02:22.39,0:02:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Twinkling in the wind... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:02:40.91,0:02:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a world of unreality,{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:02:46.20,0:02:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing more than an imprinted vision.{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:02:53.13,0:03:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Point at Infinity{\i}\N{\i1}Where those values lie overwritten by this inert universe{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:03.97,0:03:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If God in his arrogance reigns through lightspeed unseen,{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:13.69,0:03:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I alone{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:19.03,0:03:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will be the miraculous...{\i}\N{\i1}the fatal... minority.{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:25.78,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can fly high{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:26.87,0:03:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that moment, if that place was{\i}\N{\i1}something you thought was special to you{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:32.79,0:03:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All those moments and places{\i}\N{\i1}If you think they're special,{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:37.55,0:03:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those invaluable scenes{\i}\N{\i1}will eclipse the heartache{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:43.05,0:03:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As each and every light forms to yield Zero.{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:48.60,0:03:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no God. Wonderful new world.{\i}
Dialogue: 30,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe-kun!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Izaki?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:01.74,0:04:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, that report of yours\Nwas pretty darn impressive!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:05.66,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:07.87,0:04:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you thinking about studying abroad?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:10.62,0:04:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, tentatively...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:13.37,0:04:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, you had me worried,
Dialogue: 30,0:04:15.38,0:04:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but based on your work as of late,\Nyou might just pull it off.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:20.13,0:04:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it the good work.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:22.05,0:04:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I will! Thank you!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:27.18,0:04:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kagari-san? Want some\NJuicy Chicken Number One?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—It's Mayushii's favorite food ever!\N—Oh!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:34.44,0:04:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—You don't mind?\N—Hmm...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:35.77,0:04:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—Nope! It's super tasty,\Nso I wanted you to try some too!\N—Hmm, hmm...
Dialogue: 30,0:04:40.98,0:04:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I think I will.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:44.99,0:04:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very welcome!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some, Daru-kun?
Dialogue: 30,0:04:48.74,0:04:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll eat some.
Dialogue: 30,0:04:50.16,0:04:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Gimme just a minute!
Dialogue: 30,0:04:54.87,0:05:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ There's just one thing I'm searching for... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:05:00.46,0:05:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The laughter of the stars... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:05:06.13,0:05:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Twinkling in— ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:05:08.05,0:05:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That song... I know it.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:11.31,0:05:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:14.48,0:05:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long ago... Somewhere...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Whoa!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:23.86,0:05:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari-san! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari-san!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri! How's Kagari?!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:35.58,0:05:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 30,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said she collapsed again?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:40.59,0:05:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, she's sleeping.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuha...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have a word?
Dialogue: 30,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 30,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:55.60,0:05:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you know, I'm...
Dialogue: 30,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...not aiming to reach Steins Gate.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:00.02,0:06:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:00.98,0:06:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell without you saying.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:09.11,0:06:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll ever come back?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:11.53,0:06:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:12.58,0:06:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari's memories.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:14.29,0:06:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the girl's a war orphan.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:19.37,0:06:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never knew her parents' faces...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:21.46,0:06:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Had nothing but painful memories, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:24.92,0:06:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, her meeting Big Sis Mayu\Nchanged her life forever.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:30.51,0:06:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Big Sis Mayu,\Nshe finally learned how to smile.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:36.73,0:06:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she ran away from me...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:39.35,0:06:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she pointed a gun at me.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:43.11,0:06:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying if the worldline changed,\Nshe couldn't meet Mommy anymore.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:47.07,0:06:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was just 10 years old...
Dialogue: 30,0:06:50.95,0:06:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might get her memories back,\Nor she might not.
Dialogue: 30,0:06:54.49,0:06:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for her, I wonder which\Nis the happier outcome?
Dialogue: 30,0:06:59.04,0:07:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If her memory does come back,
Dialogue: 30,0:07:00.42,0:07:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she might remember something about the\Npeople who attacked her, so there's always that.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:06.71,0:07:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I plan to do all that\NI can do, and that hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:15.10,0:07:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Kagari, all right?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:22.65,0:07:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ There's just one thing I'm searching for... ♪
Dialogue: 30,0:07:29.07,0:07:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—♪ The laughter of the stars... ♪\N—Mommy? Mommy!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 30,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—Huh?\N—Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:37.08,0:07:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, um...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:39.66,0:07:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did it... happen again?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all right?
Dialogue: 30,0:07:43.71,0:07:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 30,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri left just a bit ago.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:50.92,0:07:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess they didn't have enough people\Nto cover the lunchtime rush.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:55.51,0:07:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu-shi was worried sick about you.
Dialogue: 30,0:07:58.18,0:08:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:04.48,0:08:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feel a little better now?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:07.32,0:08:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a song.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:10.28,0:08:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, my head just...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A song?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:14.66,0:08:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard that song before?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:16.99,0:08:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:17.99,0:08:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not one you heard lately?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:20.08,0:08:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not, I don't think.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:22.62,0:08:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A song...
Dialogue: 30,0:08:23.96,0:08:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Okarin?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:29.34,0:08:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know. It might be a hint that\Nleads to getting your memories back.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:35.43,0:08:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not too hard on you,\Nit's something we could look into.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine with me.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay now.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:45.31,0:08:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how was your checkup?
Dialogue: 30,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm as healthy as I've always been.
Dialogue: 30,0:08:49.73,0:08:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been half a month, for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:52.40,0:08:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okarin-san doesn't have to keep\Ngoing in for checkups, so why do I?!
Dialogue: 30,0:08:59.41,0:09:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be happy to have no problems.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:01.87,0:09:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do have problems!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:04.00,0:09:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put on fat during my hospital stay\Nand it just won't come off!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:09.59,0:09:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you say we hit up some karaoke?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:12.63,0:09:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry but...
Dialogue: 30,0:09:14.34,0:09:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda have plans after this.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, shoot! I need to hurry!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do karaoke another time.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:27.15,0:09:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-san, in front of—
Dialogue: 30,0:09:29.98,0:09:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:33.07,0:09:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I can't believe how clumsy she is!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:38.62,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari-san! Are you better now?!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:41.37,0:09:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sorry to have worried you.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:44.37,0:09:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mayushii is sorry for not\Nbeing able to stay at your side!
Dialogue: 30,0:09:51.13,0:09:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A song?
Dialogue: 30,0:09:52.05,0:09:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's that song you were singing earlier.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:55.88,0:09:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've heard it somewhere.
Dialogue: 30,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember where you learned it from?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:01.30,0:10:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's possible that song is a hint\Nto get Kagari's memories back.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, let's see...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:07.94,0:10:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii first heard that song from Suzu-san!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:11.52,0:10:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Suzuha?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:12.61,0:10:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! I sometimes hear Suzu-san singing\Nthat song while looking out the window.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:18.40,0:10:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So unfortunately, Mayushii doesn't\Nknow the name of the song.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:24.49,0:10:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's a song that's popular in the future?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:27.50,0:10:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I couldn't be of any help.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you for telling us.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:33.09,0:10:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin? Are you planning to visit Suzu-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Yeah, to check with her.
Dialogue: 30,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Mayushii come too?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:41.55,0:10:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:43.76,0:10:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, it's hard to explain, but...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:47.02,0:10:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I look at Kagari-san,\NMayushii just wants to do everything I can to help!
Dialogue: 30,0:10:52.19,0:10:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:54.27,0:10:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about work?
Dialogue: 30,0:10:57.86,0:11:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The peak has passed, so it's fine, nya!
Dialogue: 30,0:11:01.03,0:11:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, I'll give Suzuha a ring.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be working.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:11.29,0:11:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that was the case,\Nshe should be on lunch break.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:14.25,0:11:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed Suzu-nya outside a bit ago.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:17.21,0:11:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:21.43,0:11:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? Suzu-nya?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sis Rumi?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:24.97,0:11:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the scary-looking face?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:29.48,0:11:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:31.52,0:11:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to head into battle.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:34.86,0:11:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle?
Dialogue: 30,0:11:35.94,0:11:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what she said, nya.
Dialogue: 30,0:11:39.36,0:11:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 30,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible... Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:08.89,0:12:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This month's eating contest winner is...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:12.14,0:12:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first three-time winner,\NThe Silent Slaughterer!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not even stuffed yet.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat what you can when you can.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:24.11,0:12:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an important rule to live by\Nfor survival on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You had me worried there.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 30,0:12:33.62,0:12:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe you heard me singing.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:35.96,0:12:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very cute of you!
Dialogue: 30,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please spare me, Big Sis Mayu.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:40.51,0:12:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember where\Nyou heard that song, Suzuha?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:44.26,0:12:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo—
Dialogue: 30,0:12:45.30,0:12:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Yuki-san was singing it.
Dialogue: 30,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-san was?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:54.35,0:12:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you heard it from Yuki-san,\Nyou mean in the future?
Dialogue: 30,0:12:57.77,0:13:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Mom was always singing\Nwhen she cooked our meals.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:01.73,0:13:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's possible that Kagari learned\Nit from you or Yuki-san too?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not possible.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:08.70,0:13:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari was adopted by\NBig Sis Mayu only after Mom died.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:13.41,0:13:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never sang in front of Kagari either.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:18.04,0:13:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagari from Mayuri... Mayuri from Suzuha...\NSuzuha learned it from Yuki-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:25.05,0:13:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just like the telephone game...
Dialogue: 30,0:13:29.05,0:13:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:30.14,0:13:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, maybe Yuki-san is working.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:33.10,0:13:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. We'll just have\Nto wait until she calls back.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Okabe-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:38.86,0:13:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—Over there...\N—Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:41.02,0:13:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's Yuki-san!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:43.82,0:13:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... She's together with... Daru?!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:46.90,0:13:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's some sauce on the side of your mouth.
Dialogue: 30,0:13:53.91,0:13:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll wipe it myself!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:56.46,0:14:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't try cleaning my disgusting face\Nor it'll ruin your handkerchief!
Dialogue: 30,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. Hold still, okay?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not disgusting at all.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey! Are they on a date?!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a date!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:12.22,0:14:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those two are seeing each other?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:14.64,0:14:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rascal, saying he had somewhere to be...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:18.06,0:14:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What to do, Okarin?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't get in their way.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:21.98,0:14:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll ask later. Is that okay, Kagari?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:24.82,0:14:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, though...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:31.62,0:14:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry for intruding...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:35.79,0:14:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be. Like they say, the more the merrier.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, about that song...
Dialogue: 30,0:14:45.42,0:14:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well you see, I sometimes help out\Nteaching at a baking class.
Dialogue: 30,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:51.01,0:14:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki-san makes the most\Ndelicious sweets you'll ever have!
Dialogue: 30,0:14:54.81,0:14:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:55.89,0:14:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we make some together next time?
Dialogue: 30,0:14:58.68,0:15:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:00.23,0:15:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:01.90,0:15:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that have to do with the song?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:04.27,0:15:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the students that comes\Nto our class is always singing it.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sing that song?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:10.74,0:15:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:11.91,0:15:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before long, it got stuck in my head.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:14.16,0:15:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that person who\Nsang it is someone we know?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:17.41,0:15:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not so sure. I'd say they're\Nsome 20 years older than us.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not seeming very likely then.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:26.17,0:15:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I thought\Nit'd be easier just to ask.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:30.17,0:15:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I'll put him on.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:36.01,0:15:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, sorry about this.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:38.18,0:15:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Okabe, a friend of Amane-san's.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:40.64,0:15:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okabe?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:41.52,0:15:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. To be honest,\NI just wanted to ask about that song.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:46.32,0:15:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice... Is that you, Rintaro?
Dialogue: 30,0:15:49.15,0:15:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—Huh?\N—It's me! Me!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:52.11,0:15:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice! It can't be!
Dialogue: 30,0:15:54.28,0:15:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me? Don't tell me you forgot\Nthe beautiful voice of your own mother.
Dialogue: 30,0:15:59.91,0:16:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the lady turned\Nout to be your mother...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:04.13,0:16:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In class, we all just use\Neveryone's first names.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:07.04,0:16:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What did your mother have to say?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:10.26,0:16:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 30,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From you!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:13.18,0:16:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:13.76,0:16:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, you're the one who sang it!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I did?!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:18.06,0:16:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?\NI don't even know the song!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:21.18,0:16:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? Back when you were in middle school\Nand Mayuri-chan was down in the dumps?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:27.77,0:16:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was around the time\Nyou started acting all weird.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:30.99,0:16:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, what was it again?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:33.20,0:16:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a macho psychologist!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:37.83,0:16:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:38.45,0:16:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, that's what you used\Nto sing all the time in the bath.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:42.96,0:16:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:44.08,0:16:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! And because of you,\NI can't forget it!
Dialogue: 30,0:16:47.59,0:16:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what exactly does this mean?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:52.59,0:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't recall ever singing\Nthat song in the first place.
Dialogue: 30,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard him sing it, Mayuri-san?
Dialogue: 30,0:16:58.68,0:17:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayushii doesn't remember that either.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:02.77,0:17:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all stuck in the same spot as Kagari now.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:06.56,0:17:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, did I hear that right about\NMayuri-san being down in the dumps?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:12.32,0:17:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, stuff happened.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:14.20,0:17:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Okarin. Do you think we should go?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:18.07,0:17:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go? You mean there?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:20.37,0:17:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You never know!\NMaybe you'll remember something!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:32.96,0:17:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma will be so happy\Nyou came to visit, Okarin.
Dialogue: 30,0:17:37.22,0:17:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to see your grandma?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:39.55,0:17:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! And I'll introduce you\Nto her too, Kagari-san!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And tell her you're Mayushii's beloved friend!
Dialogue: 30,0:17:46.77,0:17:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayuri-san...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:52.86,0:17:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Okarin? Do you remember anything?
Dialogue: 30,0:17:56.20,0:17:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 30,0:17:59.49,0:18:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll talk to your grandma, right?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:02.29,0:18:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:03.95,0:18:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'll only be a minute.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:10.92,0:18:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Grandma.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:13.63,0:18:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess what? I made a\Nnew friend named Kagari-san!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:18.22,0:18:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—This is like a ritual for her.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:18.22,0:18:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—But the thing is, Kagari-san has amnesia.
Dialogue: 30,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—A ritual?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:24.35,0:18:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To lose all your memories of the past,\Nthat has to be so sad...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:30.31,0:18:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll get them back?
Dialogue: 30,0:18:35.69,0:18:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if they came back...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:41.82,0:18:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Mayuri, it's raining! Let's take cover!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure came pouring down...
Dialogue: 30,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're totally drenched!
Dialogue: 30,0:18:55.71,0:18:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should've brought umbrellas.
Dialogue: 30,0:19:02.26,0:19:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! We can go to Mayushii's house and—
